import { Image } from 'react-native'

export default function TelaInicial(){
    return(
        <View>
            <Image style={{width: 200, height: 100}} src='assets\logo com nome.svg'></Image>
            <TouchableOpacity style={{backgroundColor: '#5F5DEE', borderRadius: '4px', shadowColor: '#A1A1A1C2', shadowRadius: '2px 2px 8px 0px'}}>
                <Text style={{color: 'white'}}>Sou cliente</Text>
            </TouchableOpacity>

            <TouchableOpacity>
                <Text>Sou transportador</Text>
            </TouchableOpacity>

            <Text>Ao se registrar vocÃª concorda com os <Text style={{color: '#5F5DEE'}}>termos de uso.</Text></Text>
        </View>
    )
}
